1
00:00:10,135 --> 00:00:10,593
Takumi!

2
00:00:10,593 --> 00:00:10,677
Takumi!

3
00:00:14,264 --> 00:00:15,056
Čo tu....

4
00:00:20,937 --> 00:00:22,856
Krásna noc.

5
00:00:23,648 --> 00:00:28,903
Predstavujem si, ako váš tanec rozjasní oblohu.

6
00:00:31,448 --> 00:00:33,283
Však, Mai HiME?

7
00:02:08,003 --> 00:02:10,088
Á ty si HiME.

8
00:02:10,422 --> 00:02:13,383
Musí to byť zábava, klamať ostatným, že si chlapec.

9
00:02:13,425 --> 00:02:15,635
Sklapni! Čo si chcela spraviť Takumimu?

10
00:02:15,885 --> 00:02:17,929
Toto zranenie....vyzerá dosť vážne, nie?

11
00:02:18,722 --> 00:02:20,515
Ozaj to bolí.

12
00:02:21,141 --> 00:02:25,061
Spôsobila mi to jeho sestra.

13
00:02:25,812 --> 00:02:27,439
Takže, vieš kam idem.

14
00:02:32,652 --> 00:02:34,029
Zjav sa, Gennai!

15
00:02:36,406 --> 00:02:37,615
Útok Kiri Gakure!!

16
00:02:48,918 --> 00:02:51,588
Previezol som ju do nemocnice, kde bude v bezpečí.

17
00:02:52,339 --> 00:02:54,341
Vďaka za všetko.

18
00:02:56,760 --> 00:02:57,427
Stalo sa niečo?

19
00:02:58,345 --> 00:02:58,720
Nič.

20
00:03:00,013 --> 00:03:02,140
Tak...o čo tu ide?

21
00:03:02,807 --> 00:03:04,476
Propagačná sekcia Nadácie Searrs.

22
00:03:05,226 --> 00:03:08,980
Je to vlastne ich výzvedná služba.
Kontaktovali ma.

23
00:03:09,773 --> 00:03:11,358
Chcú informácie.

24
00:03:21,785 --> 00:03:22,452
Mikoto?

25
00:03:22,577 --> 00:03:23,286
Nie.

26
00:03:25,121 --> 00:03:25,914
Nao?

27
00:03:26,122 --> 00:03:32,170
Práve teraz idem po tvojom bratovi, a po tej HiME,
čo sa vydávala za chlapca.

28
00:03:33,963 --> 00:03:34,839
Takumi je...?

29
00:03:35,465 --> 00:03:36,216
Okej.

30
00:03:41,137 --> 00:03:43,390
Veci sa pohli.

31
00:03:44,099 --> 00:03:46,559
Je priskoro. Prosím, ešte nie.

32
00:03:46,559 --> 00:03:47,977
Dosiahli sme...

33
00:03:50,397 --> 00:03:51,106
Čo si to povedala?

34
00:03:51,606 --> 00:03:55,402
Nemôžu sa z nemocnice dovolať Mai, tak zavolali mne
ako jej učiteľke.

35
00:03:56,027 --> 00:03:58,571
Mám z toho zlý pocit. Pomôž mi, prosím.

36
00:03:58,863 --> 00:04:01,116
Dočerta, čo sa deje?

37
00:04:01,533 --> 00:04:02,617
Hej, a čo s našou dohodou?

38
00:04:02,867 --> 00:04:03,993
Zatial to odložíme.

39
00:04:06,454 --> 00:04:07,330
Takže povedala....

40
00:04:09,165 --> 00:04:10,041
Vieš, táto jazva...

41
00:04:11,001 --> 00:04:12,210
ozaj bolí.

42
00:04:13,586 --> 00:04:18,341
Rozhodla som sa, že ty, a Kuga Natsuki, budete trpieť
za to, čo ste mi spôsobili.

43
00:04:18,758 --> 00:04:21,219
Prosím prestaň, Takumi je môj...

44
00:04:21,344 --> 00:04:22,762
Drahý braček?

45
00:04:24,723 --> 00:04:27,142
Nieje to tak, že v skutočnosti ho nenávidíš?

46
00:04:27,976 --> 00:04:30,937
Nepriala si si, aby zmizol?

47
00:04:31,229 --> 00:04:32,272
Ako by som len mohla....?

48
00:04:32,605 --> 00:04:33,565
Tým by som si nebola tak istá.

49
00:04:33,815 --> 00:04:36,317
Si len sestra, čo sa snaží len tak tak
uživiť vás oboch.

50
00:04:36,651 --> 00:04:38,028
Mikoto to povedala tiež.

51
00:04:38,403 --> 00:04:41,990
"Vždy sa ku mne správa ako k decku."

52
00:04:43,033 --> 00:04:45,535
No, ale teraz....

53
00:04:46,202 --> 00:04:47,662
príde moja odplata, zákerná sestrička.

54
00:04:48,079 --> 00:04:50,248
Počkaj, prosím....

55
00:05:02,177 --> 00:05:03,345
Čo sa stalo Takumimu?

56
00:05:03,762 --> 00:05:08,391
Jeho izba je zničená, a nevieme, kde je.

57
00:05:11,770 --> 00:05:14,939
Tokiha sa musí ozaj báť.

58
00:05:25,158 --> 00:05:26,368
Čo sa deje?

59
00:05:26,368 --> 00:05:28,286
Čo? Ja...

60
00:05:29,746 --> 00:05:30,580
Opäť máš horúčku?

61
00:05:30,580 --> 00:05:33,332
Opäť máš horúčku?
Ak ti nieje dobre, radšej si ľahni.

62
00:05:36,753 --> 00:05:38,171
Si v poriadku, Takumi?

63
00:05:39,339 --> 00:05:39,756
Hej.

64
00:05:43,009 --> 00:05:44,135
Našla som ťa.

65
00:05:46,346 --> 00:05:49,057
Ak chceš niekoho nenávidieť, tak nenáviď svoju sestru.

66
00:05:49,974 --> 00:05:50,684
Prestaň!

67
00:05:52,852 --> 00:05:54,020
Nao, prestaň.

68
00:05:54,562 --> 00:05:55,647
Ty otravná kurva!

69
00:06:01,778 --> 00:06:03,279
Zmiznite odtiaľto, hýbte sa.

70
00:06:03,405 --> 00:06:04,322
Vrelá vďaka.

71
00:06:06,324 --> 00:06:06,866
Doriti.

72
00:06:09,703 --> 00:06:11,663
Takumi... Takumi je....

73
00:06:11,871 --> 00:06:12,706
Je to príťaž.

74
00:06:16,292 --> 00:06:18,253
V skutočnosti ho nenávidíš, nie?

75
00:06:18,712 --> 00:06:21,715
Nepriala si si, aby zmizol?

76
00:06:24,175 --> 00:06:26,302
Tak to nieje.

77
00:06:27,846 --> 00:06:28,972
Pretože som to sľúbila.

78
00:06:30,181 --> 00:06:31,766
Sľúbila som mame a ockovi....

79
00:06:32,976 --> 00:06:33,601
Mama....

80
00:06:34,686 --> 00:06:35,854
Pretože ja...

81
00:06:37,897 --> 00:06:40,984
Počuj, Takumi, počkaj tu, jasné?

82
00:06:41,359 --> 00:06:43,278
Nechoď do vody, hej?

83
00:06:47,323 --> 00:06:48,033
Pretože ja...

84
00:06:50,035 --> 00:06:52,287
nechala som Takumiho samého.

85
00:07:01,379 --> 00:07:02,464
Natsuki?

86
00:07:02,964 --> 00:07:04,341
Daj sa dohromady, Mai.

87
00:07:04,924 --> 00:07:06,718
Takumi sa stratil, však?

88
00:07:07,177 --> 00:07:08,678
Prečo ho nehľadáš?

89
00:07:09,929 --> 00:07:12,724
Ale....povedal....

90
00:07:14,476 --> 00:07:15,977
že ma nepotrebuje.

91
00:07:16,811 --> 00:07:18,521
Potom čo je to s tebou?

92
00:07:20,231 --> 00:07:23,068
Nemám nič, čo by som chránila.

93
00:07:24,152 --> 00:07:25,487
Ale ty...

94
00:07:26,780 --> 00:07:29,407
Za čo si doteraz bojovala?

95
00:07:29,824 --> 00:07:30,825
Spomeň si, Mai.

96
00:07:42,212 --> 00:07:42,712
Mai.

97
00:07:43,463 --> 00:07:44,381
Zmizni.

98
00:07:50,929 --> 00:07:51,721
To je ona?

99
00:07:53,515 --> 00:07:54,474
Napadla ma tak náhle.

100
00:07:54,808 --> 00:07:55,725
Nechaj to na mňa.

101
00:07:56,643 --> 00:07:59,354
Midori sa postará o Takumiho.

102
00:08:00,605 --> 00:08:01,189
Vďaka, Natsuki.

103
00:08:04,109 --> 00:08:06,903
Dočerta, sme tu priskoro.

104
00:08:07,445 --> 00:08:09,572
Akira, čo sa deje?

105
00:08:10,865 --> 00:08:12,951
To bola Yuuki, však?

106
00:08:13,618 --> 00:08:15,120
Vravela, že ju sestra zranila.

107
00:08:16,204 --> 00:08:16,788
Takumi.

108
00:08:17,122 --> 00:08:17,956
Chcem to vedieť.

109
00:08:18,748 --> 00:08:21,418
Nie, musím to zistiť.

110
00:08:22,335 --> 00:08:22,836
Jasné?

111
00:08:25,046 --> 00:08:25,839
Dobre.

112
00:08:27,132 --> 00:08:29,676
Tvoja sestra je tiež HiME.

113
00:08:31,302 --> 00:08:32,429
Tak ako ja.

114
00:08:32,887 --> 00:08:33,430
Čo?

115
00:08:35,640 --> 00:08:39,811
A chce zabrániť ostatným HiME, aby bojovali
medzi sebou.

116
00:08:40,895 --> 00:08:46,067
Keď je HiME porazená, tak osoba, ktorú mala
najradšej prestane existovať.

117
00:08:46,526 --> 00:08:49,779
Takže....ak by som prehral...

118
00:08:51,156 --> 00:08:52,574
Bola by to tvoja smrť.

119
00:08:53,283 --> 00:08:53,908
Neviem.

120
00:08:55,118 --> 00:08:57,537
Dočerta, keby som len....

121
00:08:58,079 --> 00:09:02,667
Si tak slabý, a jednoduchý....

122
00:09:07,756 --> 00:09:10,383
Ale keď som s tebou, tak je všetko OK.

123
00:09:11,468 --> 00:09:15,305
Pretože si mi vrátil dôvod žiť.

124
00:09:16,222 --> 00:09:19,726
Hlupáčik.

125
00:09:21,728 --> 00:09:23,480
Nebudem prosiť o odpustenie.

126
00:09:24,522 --> 00:09:27,734
Len dúfam, že im Boh žehná.

127
00:09:28,193 --> 00:09:32,489
Rozumieš? Spôsobuj medzi nimi zmätok.

128
00:09:33,990 --> 00:09:37,660
Dieťa získa silu porazeného.

129
00:09:38,536 --> 00:09:42,207
No sila Mai je trocha odlišná.

130
00:09:43,083 --> 00:09:50,507
Takže musíme pripraviť Mai o toho, koho má najradšej
ak keď nebude mať svoje Dieťa, Yuuki, ju porazí.

131
00:09:51,299 --> 00:09:54,552
Takto odstránime najväčšiu prekážku.

132
00:09:55,845 --> 00:09:57,138
Kvôli záchrane sveta....

133
00:09:57,681 --> 00:10:00,058
a aby si sa stala najsilnejšou HiME.

134
00:10:02,227 --> 00:10:03,687
Nechcem nič takého....

135
00:10:07,982 --> 00:10:11,820
Lord Kokuyou, môžem ťa premôcť.

136
00:10:12,570 --> 00:10:14,989
Bude mi patriť sila Hviezdy.

137
00:10:17,701 --> 00:10:18,660
Kto si?

138
00:10:19,411 --> 00:10:20,620
Prečo chceš zabiť Mai?

139
00:10:21,413 --> 00:10:23,206
Ty nie!

140
00:10:31,673 --> 00:10:32,007
Dokelu.

141
00:10:36,761 --> 00:10:38,888
Všetci sa držte ďalej.

142
00:10:39,681 --> 00:10:41,808
Celé to tu evakuujeme.

143
00:10:41,808 --> 00:10:42,183
Shizuru.

144
00:10:42,392 --> 00:10:42,684
Natsuki.

145
00:10:42,684 --> 00:10:42,934
Natsuki.

146
00:10:43,643 --> 00:10:44,185
Poďme.

147
00:10:47,731 --> 00:10:49,024
Čo ti to furt tak trvá?

148
00:10:49,441 --> 00:10:50,358
Pohni si, a vylez.

149
00:10:50,442 --> 00:10:52,652
A-Ale ja...

150
00:10:52,736 --> 00:10:54,154
Pozbieraj sa, Yukino.

151
00:10:54,988 --> 00:10:56,740
Sme predsa študentská rada.

152
00:10:58,324 --> 00:11:02,746
Udržujeme poriadok a mier v škole, nie?

153
00:11:03,788 --> 00:11:04,539
Hej.

154
00:11:05,707 --> 00:11:07,584
Vyzerá to, že už je ti lepšie.

155
00:11:08,209 --> 00:11:09,294
Poďme, Yukino.

156
00:11:10,587 --> 00:11:11,379
Haruka.

157
00:11:14,924 --> 00:11:16,676
Suzushiro, požičiam si ju na chvíľu.

158
00:11:27,103 --> 00:11:27,812
To je.....

159
00:11:41,117 --> 00:11:43,536
Dočerta, prečo tu stále blúdime?

160
00:11:45,538 --> 00:11:48,083
Vydrž, čoskoro bude po všetkom.

161
00:11:55,256 --> 00:11:57,175
Počítam s tebou. Takumi je v nebezpečenstve.

162
00:11:58,426 --> 00:11:59,052
Mai.

163
00:12:02,222 --> 00:12:02,722
Tam je.

164
00:12:04,265 --> 00:12:06,518
Pohni si.

165
00:12:07,477 --> 00:12:08,103
Okej.

166
00:12:10,814 --> 00:12:12,941
Vďaka, Yukino.

167
00:12:15,026 --> 00:12:17,362
Ozaj ma to mrzí.

168
00:12:18,238 --> 00:12:18,822
Prepáč.

169
00:12:20,782 --> 00:12:22,742
Takumi, Akira.

170
00:12:23,618 --> 00:12:25,245
Ochránim ich.

171
00:12:27,539 --> 00:12:28,331
Akira.

172
00:12:28,915 --> 00:12:30,166
Takumi. Akira.

173
00:12:34,462 --> 00:12:35,213
Mikoto?

174
00:12:39,384 --> 00:12:40,218
Sestra!

175
00:12:43,388 --> 00:12:44,973
Uteč, Gennai.

176
00:13:01,573 --> 00:13:02,574
Takumi....

177
00:13:05,201 --> 00:13:06,286
Akira!

178
00:13:08,371 --> 00:13:08,830
Takumi!

179
00:13:11,166 --> 00:13:11,708
Takumi!

180
00:13:14,044 --> 00:13:18,006
Nie, Takumi.....Nie....

181
00:13:19,883 --> 00:13:21,134
Sestra...

182
00:13:21,760 --> 00:13:24,429
Žartuješ, však? Ty predsa nemôžeš...

183
00:13:26,598 --> 00:13:28,808
Prepáč....

184
00:13:29,893 --> 00:13:31,353
Ďakujem ti.

185
00:13:35,857 --> 00:13:38,276
NIEEEEE!!!!

186
00:13:47,911 --> 00:13:50,663
Ako to...

187
00:13:53,333 --> 00:13:54,042
Prečo?

188
00:14:06,638 --> 00:14:07,097
Mai?

189
00:14:10,016 --> 00:14:10,892
Mikoto.

190
00:14:20,902 --> 00:14:22,320
Prečo si zabila Takumiho?

191
00:14:23,446 --> 00:14:25,281
Takumi?

192
00:14:26,116 --> 00:14:27,158
Čo sa mu stalo?

193
00:14:32,956 --> 00:14:34,374
Zabila si ho!!!

194
00:14:36,126 --> 00:14:38,670
Zabila si...Takumiho!

195
00:14:42,882 --> 00:14:43,883
Kagutsuchi!

196
00:14:52,767 --> 00:14:53,893
Kagutsuchi.

197
00:14:54,853 --> 00:14:55,520
Prečo?

198
00:14:56,354 --> 00:14:58,440
Ja...

199
00:15:00,567 --> 00:15:04,946
Premohla som Akiru?

200
00:15:10,076 --> 00:15:13,872
Preto je Mai smutná?

201
00:15:16,791 --> 00:15:19,044
Potom sa nedá už nič robiť.

202
00:15:28,928 --> 00:15:29,596
Stratila ho.

203
00:15:30,221 --> 00:15:30,764
Natsuki.

204
00:15:36,311 --> 00:15:37,187
Mai.

205
00:15:38,438 --> 00:15:40,314
Doriti s tou štetkou.

206
00:15:42,650 --> 00:15:43,735
Nestihla som to včas.

207
00:15:45,070 --> 00:15:48,541
Nestihla som to zastaviť.

208
00:15:49,366 --> 00:15:50,325
Mashiro.

209
00:15:56,122 --> 00:15:57,916
Čože? Ako je to možné?

210
00:16:02,003 --> 00:16:03,213
Výborne, Mai.

211
00:16:03,838 --> 00:16:05,674
Si najlepšia.

212
00:16:10,762 --> 00:16:12,889
Netrafilo ma to?

213
00:16:13,973 --> 00:16:15,308
Mikoto!

214
00:16:28,405 --> 00:16:31,032
Mai na mňa útočí.

215
00:16:31,700 --> 00:16:33,326
A tí ktorí útočia sú nepriatelia.

216
00:16:35,787 --> 00:16:38,289
Správne, Mai je nepriateľ.

217
00:16:38,998 --> 00:16:40,500
Musíš poraziť napriateľov.

218
00:16:41,835 --> 00:16:45,505
Správne, musím ich poraziť.

219
00:17:04,816 --> 00:17:07,902
Nemôžem to už ďalej skrývať....

220
00:17:11,489 --> 00:17:12,782
Pohnite si, všetci do bezpečia.

221
00:17:13,116 --> 00:17:14,200
Nepostávajte tu len tak.

222
00:17:14,659 --> 00:17:15,493
Čo je to?

223
00:17:15,952 --> 00:17:16,703
Drak?

224
00:17:19,039 --> 00:17:21,666
Netáraj a pohni si.

225
00:17:24,044 --> 00:17:24,544
Duran!

226
00:17:28,631 --> 00:17:31,843
Vieš vôbec, čo robíš?

227
00:17:31,843 --> 00:17:32,469
Viem!

228
00:17:33,011 --> 00:17:35,638
Mikoto...Mikoto zabila Takumiho!

229
00:17:38,224 --> 00:17:39,392
Okuzaki Akira?

230
00:18:06,294 --> 00:18:06,753
Dieťa?

231
00:18:06,753 --> 00:18:06,920
Dieťa?

232
00:18:07,796 --> 00:18:08,380
Ale koho?

233
00:18:09,005 --> 00:18:10,382
Mikoto!!

234
00:18:17,055 --> 00:18:18,056
Prestaň Mikoto!

235
00:18:18,598 --> 00:18:21,810
To je Mai. Vravela si, že ju máš rada.

236
00:18:22,936 --> 00:18:23,687
Rada?

237
00:18:27,565 --> 00:18:27,982
Mai.

238
00:18:27,982 --> 00:18:28,900
Mai....

239
00:18:39,994 --> 00:18:41,663
Milujem Mai.

240
00:18:41,913 --> 00:18:43,832
Láska je dobrá.

241
00:18:45,917 --> 00:18:47,544
Ja...

242
00:18:48,962 --> 00:18:51,756
Výborne, porazila si ma.

243
00:18:52,549 --> 00:18:54,134
Takto by to malo byť.

244
00:18:54,509 --> 00:19:02,017
Aj keď smieš milovať iba svojho brata, Lorda Kokuyou.

245
00:19:03,560 --> 00:19:06,354
Ako si len vyrástla.

246
00:19:07,313 --> 00:19:10,316
Je z teba veľká HiME.

247
00:19:11,192 --> 00:19:16,489
Zabila som starkého, ktorého som mala rada, svojimi
vlastnými rukami.

248
00:19:17,949 --> 00:19:26,458
Nemáš ani poňatia, aké to je, niekoho ozaj milovať.

249
00:19:27,292 --> 00:19:28,251
Nikdy...

250
00:19:29,169 --> 00:19:33,381
som nikoho nemilovala.

251
00:19:38,553 --> 00:19:39,304
Mikoto?

252
00:19:42,140 --> 00:19:42,849
Kagutsuchi!

253
00:19:43,641 --> 00:19:45,143
Počkaj!!

254
00:19:51,608 --> 00:19:53,443
Mikoto!!

255
00:20:08,583 --> 00:20:10,794
Mikoto..

256
